trans-unit.source: Supports a simple iteration over a binding collection in an application upgraded from Visual Basic 6.0.
trans-unit.target: 支持在从 Visual Basic 6.0 升级的应用程序中的绑定集合上进行简单迭代。

trans-unit.source: When an application is upgraded to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], a `BindingCollectionEnumerator` is created to enable the `ADO`-related code.
trans-unit.target: 在应用程序升级到[!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]、`BindingCollectionEnumerator`创建以启用`ADO`-相关的代码。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Functions and objects in the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> namespace are provided for use by the tools for upgrading from Visual Basic 6.0 to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 1> [!NOTE] 1> 函数和对象在<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>命名空间提供用于连接的工具从到 Visual Basic 6.0 升级[!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]。</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>

trans-unit.source: In most cases, these functions and objects duplicate functionality that you can find in other namespaces in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 在大多数情况下，这些函数和对象重复可在其他命名空间中找到的功能[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: They are necessary only when the Visual Basic 6.0 code model differs significantly from the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementation.
trans-unit.target: 仅当 Visual Basic 6.0 代码模型显著区别它们是所必需[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]实现。

trans-unit.source: Gets the current element in the binding collection.
trans-unit.target: 获取绑定集合中的当前元素。

trans-unit.source: The current element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的当前元素。

trans-unit.source: Advances the enumerator to the next element of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举数推进到集合的下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the enumerator has passed the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果枚举数已成功地推进到下一个元素;，<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>如果枚举数传递到集合的末尾。

trans-unit.source: Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举数设置为其初始位置，集合中第一个元素之前。
